data.description: Allow us to present this exquisite 2 unit multi family  property located in the Englewood neighborhood. Its prime location provides convenient access to essential amenities like grocery stores, bus lines, and highways. Notably, the current tenants are on a month-to-month lease and receive government funding through the CHA program, ensuring guaranteed rent.    Moreover, this property is just a few minutes away from Kennedy King College and Garfield Boulevard. You can be confident that this property meets all FHA guidelines, ensuring a secure investment.
